Comment.Content: Reset the Gyro Sensor so that 0° is straight ahead.
Go straight until the color sensor sees nothing, blue, green, yellow, red, or brown.
Go straight until the color sensor sees black twice.
Go straight until the color sensor sees white.
Go slightly slower until the color sensor sees black again.
Stop the motors in front of Escape Velocity.
Hit the lever and send the ship flying.
Next mission!
Turn the robot -45° to go around Escape Velocity.
Go straight until the color sensor sees white.
Continue until the color sensor sees black.
Go slightly slower until the color sensor sees white again.
Go straight for 45° rotation of the wheels.
Turn to 30° to line up with Observatory.
Go straight to push Observatory
Reset Motor B for precise reverse movement.
Next mission!
Move the robot backwards fo 350° rotation of the wheels.
Turn to -90° to line up with Food Production.
Go straight to push in the bar to green.
Reset Motor B for precise reverse movement.
Next mission!
Move the robot backwards fo 225° rotation of the wheels.
Turn to - 30° to reverse to the base.
Aim at the base.
Reverse until the base is found.
Move into the base.
Turn off the wheels for adjusting the bar.
Unlock the bar.
Wait for the enter button to be pushed to alert the robot to do the next mission.
